{"tid":2407200,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"內地無良商人推「動物盲盒」 10蚊人仔抽哥基犬動保人士鬧爆：人渣都不如｜ 蘋果","createTime":"2021-02-13T22:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-14T00:18:38.000Z","uid":158680,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"94440420e7b099fd372cd53e371673db694f8c4f","tid":2407200,"uid":158680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T22:59:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210124/V3MYT6YG35BDTGSM4UITU67NTA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210124%2FV3MYT6YG35BDTGSM4UITU67NTA%2F&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLucwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=246346b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210124%2FV3MYT6YG35BDTGSM4UITU67NTA%2F&h=82250231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210124/V3MYT6YG35BDTGSM4UITU67NTA/</a><br />\n<br />\nOld news<br />\n內地網絡經濟發達，衣食住行的商品都可以網購。但有無良商人竟然想到，以抽「盲盒」的形式出售寵物，最平僅需9.9元人民幣（下同，約11.8港元）就有機會獲得哥基、金毛尋回犬等名種狗或貓、烏龜、兔子。令人咋舌的是，這些活體盲盒竟有數千宗成交量，有香港動保人士向《蘋果》表示，擔心無良商人為求賺錢，薄利多銷，未來或會出現棄養潮。"},{"pid":"09a36c8d254b55a4679899b1234529a6e0ee56c6","tid":2407200,"uid":22310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T00:18:38.000Z","msg":"地獄鬼國"}]}